ANDERSON
v.
KILBANE 2019-0323 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 22, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINION

On relator's "motion for stay hearing set for March 8, 2019," "motion comparison of two cases with the same criminal cause of action," and motion to convert to a writ of prohibition. Motions denied as moot. Respondent's motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.
